==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Sea leopard
<hw>Sea" leop"ard</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>Any one of
several species of spotted seals, especially <spn>Ogmorhinus
leptonyx</spn>, and <spn>Leptonychotes Weddelli</spn>, of the Antarctic
Ocean. The North Pacific sea leopard is the harbor seal.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Sealer</ent>⟦br⟧
